{"tid":2294763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林明禎家姐林詩枝貼泳照為趙碩之慶生　網民：久違了的性感女神！","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T11:22:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea6a847ad3e3c5c8cc25e984b4826220c05093e","tid":2294763,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"「大馬女神」林明禎擁有甜美面孔加驕人身形，她的姐姐林詩枝（Brandy）絲毫不比妹妹遜色，個人IG更坐擁19萬粉絲。日前（18/11）是Brandy好姊妹趙碩之的33歲生日，即使疫情令二人分隔兩地，Brandy仍未忘在社交平台貼出合照為對方送上祝福：「Happy Birthday baby Wylie. Miss you much much.」相中的Brandy和趙碩之穿上連身低胸<br />\n<br />\n泳衣，齊齊大曬Fit爆身形，網民指這是昔日「性感女神」趙碩之久違了的泳照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201120/406573511943917568587293.jpeg/TC6Co1m-SSGDf5DBdWsN_-I2uLz0DJ6D6JMou-iTKLs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201120%2F406573511943917568587293.jpeg%2FTC6Co1m-SSGDf5DBdWsN_-I2uLz0DJ6D6JMou-iTKLs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d04dacdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c58adb2080eb2985ff5ee8455408623b744f455","tid":2294763,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201120/406573652264357888450816.jpeg/H5IP0yBrbj7B7AS7-WwJIW_7bnQw_vwKAXYA8wF2APM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201120%2F406573652264357888450816.jpeg%2FH5IP0yBrbj7B7AS7-WwJIW_7bnQw_vwKAXYA8wF2APM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2137ff0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201119/406110052529737728275841.jpeg/wpGh07Tb_TuXdviato1_NgjUtsLe18rbfdryzX3a8s0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201119%2F406110052529737728275841.jpeg%2FwpGh07Tb_TuXdviato1_NgjUtsLe18rbfdryzX3a8s0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=189869ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20